---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_AUTHOR, SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={`策略框架 | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    <style>
      .intro { padding: 3rem 0 1rem; max-width: 860px; }
      .intro p { color: rgb(var(--gray)); font-size: 1.14rem; }
      .weight-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem; }
      .weight { padding: 1.1rem; }
      .weight strong { display: block; font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0.25rem 0; }
      .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin: 1rem 0 2rem; }
      .card { padding: 1.25rem; }
      .card h2, .card h3 { margin-top: 0; }
      @media (max-width: 820px) { .weight-grid, .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <section class="intro">
        <span class="pill pill-red">由 {SITE_AUTHOR} 维护</span>
        <h1>A股ETF轮动策略框架</h1>
        <p>这个站点记录每日ETF板块预测、次日复盘、命中率和权重修正。目标是把盘面动量、资金流、收盘位置、成交量和新闻风险放进同一套可复盘的流程。</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>当前评分权重</h2>
        <div class="weight-grid">
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill">动量</span><strong>25%</strong><p>近3日强度，代表短线情绪。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill">趋势</span><strong>20%</strong><p>近5日强度，代表趋势延续。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill">资金</span><strong>20%</strong><p>主力净流入和承接力度。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill">收盘</span><strong>15%</strong><p>收盘价在日内区间的位置。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill">量能</span><strong>10%</strong><p>成交额相对前5日均值。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill pill-amber">新闻</span><strong>10%</strong><p>政策催化、监管关注和溢价风险。</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="two-col">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>三类机会</h2>
          <h3>趋势延续</h3>
          <p>近5日强、资金承接、收盘靠高位，适合顺势持有或回踩低吸。</p>
          <h3>分歧修复</h3>
          <p>前期强势后出现大跌、监管或资金分歧，只看反抽确认。</p>
          <h3>轮动补涨</h3>
          <p>位置偏低、资金刚回流、新闻有修复逻辑，适合等待回踩承接。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h2>复盘方法</h2>
          <ol>
            <li>记录预测Top 5。</li>
            <li>收盘后拉取实际涨幅Top 5。</li>
            <li>计算命中数量和预测组合平均收益。</li>
            <li>检查新闻遗漏、资金背离、高位过热和低位补涨。</li>
            <li>更新下一轮权重。</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="notice">
        <strong>每日同步约定</strong>
        <p>预测、盘中修正和收盘复盘进入正式结论后，同步写入博客；首页“当前观察队列”跟随最新交易窗口更新。A股行情主用腾讯快照和东方财富补充，港股与市场状态使用 moomoo/Futu OpenD，只读执行。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="notice">
        <strong>免责声明</strong>
        <p>本站内容为 {SITE_AUTHOR} 的个人研究记录，用于复盘ETF轮动框架和交易纪律，不构成投资建议。</p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
